<plot>Korea has become a war zone when the president is assumed dead and Song, a ruthless dictator, takes over. Suddenly, the Allied Nations, China, the Russian Mafia, and South Korea are all engaged in this war, and all hating each other. In order to attempt to restore peace, the Allies send in a mercenary who can work with all 4 factions to take down the Deck of 52, the codename for Song's 51 generals, along with Song himself as the Ace of Spades. What's in it for the mercenary? A $100,000,000 bounty on Song if taken alive. Time to load your gun and join the fight.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?366255</url></doc>
